## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of comprehensive data on the number of deported veterans, as ICE does not maintain complete records. Additionally, the political and legal landscape surrounding immigration and deportation is continually evolving, which may affect the applicability of current findings. Further research and updated data are necessary for a more comprehensive understanding of this issue.